+CCC Abort fixed by:
+CCC1998-04-21  Jim Wilson  <wilson@cygnus.com>
+CCC
+CCC        * stmt.c (check_seenlabel): When search for line number note for
+CCC        warning, handle case where there is no such note.
+      logical l(10)
+      integer i(10)
+      goto (10,20),l
+      goto (10,20),i
+ 10   stop
+ 20   end
